         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">36 Hotham St E[…] ¶ 23 June 1877 ¶ My dear Sir ¶  ¶ In reply to your N28[2]7 — I have no objection to serve on the Board ¶ I remain...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">77.06.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">Mark King to William Odgers</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">M77/7138, unit 1086, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>36 Hotham St E[…]</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">23 June 1877</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to your N28[2]7 — I have no objection to serve on the Board<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">A draft of the objectives of the Board is included in the file: <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Board (Govt Botanist's Duties &amp;c)</hi>
                     </seg> To enquire into the present position of Dr Mueller in relation to his professional duties with the view to advise as to what alteration if any is necessary to afford him reasonable facilities for the due discharge of his scientific labours."' Copies of this letter were sent to L. L. Smith, J. Bosisto and M. King.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I remain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours sincy</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M L King</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">To W H Odgers Esq.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Under Secretary<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">cover sheet shows that letters were sent to MPs Smith, King, Bosisto </seg>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">
                        <hi rend="underline">and to M</hi>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; "> on 26/6/77 Q 556-62. Get at PRO.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
